1
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:03,000
Wait.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:04,420
Let go of me.

3
00:00:05,380 --> 00:00:08,340
It's not what you think.
Kamiki-san and I were just on a business trip.

4
00:00:08,340 --> 00:00:11,090
Enough.

5
00:00:11,090 --> 00:00:12,850
I've reached my limit.

6
00:00:14,310 --> 00:00:17,480
I'm a student,
and you're working.

7
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:20,020
We have different values.

8
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:26,990
Watching you work so hard...

9
00:00:26,990 --> 00:00:28,860
I feel like I'm being left behind.

10
00:00:33,490 --> 00:00:36,700
I'm scared of you becoming an adult.

11
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:41,790
I feel like I'll get left behind again.

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:46,880
Like maybe one day, you won't come back.

13
00:00:53,340 --> 00:00:56,810
I'm tired of waiting for you.

14
00:00:58,680 --> 00:00:59,930
Goodbye.
